e: 3, label: \"Step Reason Logs\", description: \"Full context maps, document scores, and model reasoning thoughts are stored inside an IT ledger.\" },\n211 |           { score: 4, label: \"Deterministic Trace\", description: \"Every execution path is recorded on a secure ledger, with cryptographically signed action chains.\" }\n212 |         ]\n213 |       },\n214 |       {\n215 |         id: \"governance_q3\",\n216 |         text: \"What is your approach to AI bias, hallucinations, and red-teaming?\",\n217 |         options: [\n218 |           { score: 1, label: \"Reactive Fixes\", description: \"Errors or biased outputs are only investigated and patched after users or clients complain.\" },\n219 |           { score: 2, label: \"Manual Spot-Checking\", description: \"Operations teams manually review a small random percentage of transcripts once a month.\" },\n220 |           { score: 3, label: \"Continuous Eval Sets\", description: \"Automated regression tests run updated validation data against models prior to deployment.\" },\n221 |           { score: 4, label: \"Adversarial Stress\", description: \"Automated simulator models constantly attack system nodes to reveal security anomalies.\" }\n222 |         ]\n223 |       }\n224 |     ]\n225 |   },\n226 |   {\n227 |     id: \"techstack\",\n228 |     name: \"Technology & Infrastructure Stack\",\n229 |     shortName: \"Tech Stack\",\n230 |     color: \"#3B82F6\",\n231 |     borderColor: \"border-[#3B82F6]/20\",\n232 |     description: \"Sovereign compute layers, model serving architectures, and zero-latency legacy software integrations.\",\n233 |     questions: [\n234 |       {\n235 |         id: \"techstack_q1\",\n236 |         text: \"What represents your core machine learning model hosting setup?\",\n237 |         options: [\n238 |           { score: 1, label: \"Public API Subscriptions\", description: \"Direct HTTP connections to standard commercial vendors; no dedicated clusters or control.\" },\n239 |          